Henry Stickmin: Infiltrating The Airship – Choose Your Path

Henry Stickmin-3: Infiltrating The Airship is the fourth installment in the Henry Stickmin series. Players make choices to help Henry infiltrate a massive airship controlled by the Toppat Clan, working alongside Captain Galeforce and Charles Calvin.

What is Henry Stickmin-3?

This point-and-click adventure has Henry choosing from various risky methods—like using an earpiece, cannonball, grapple gun, or sticky hand—to infiltrate the airship. Each choice can result in success, failure, or comical deaths, with multiple possible endings.

How to Play Henry Stickmin-3?

  • Click to Choose: Select options to progress through the airship infiltration.
  • Observe Outcomes: Choices may lead to success, humorous fails, or deadly mishaps.
  • Multiple Endings: Experiment with different strategies to reach various conclusions.
  • Replayable: Discover all possible paths and comedic fails by replaying.
